#: org.kde.audex.appdata.xml:6
msgid "Audex"
msgstr "Audex"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.audex.appdata.xml:7
msgid "Grab the audio from your CD-ROMs"
msgstr "Zgrabite zvok iz svojih CD-ROM-ov"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.audex.appdata.xml:9
msgid ""
"Audex is a CD ripper application. It lets you extract the audio from your "
"CDs to let you listen to them on your computer and your other devices. It "
"includes CDDB and MusicBrainz integrations to fetch the metadata and covers "
"for your CDs if available."
msgstr ""
"Audex je aplikacija za zajemanje CD-jev. Omogoča vam ekstrahiranje zvoka s "
"CD-jev, da jih lahko poslušate na računalniku in drugih napravah. Vključuje "
"integracijo s CDDB in MusicBrainz za pridobivanje metapodatkov in ovitkov za "
"vaše CD-je, če so na voljo."

